14:07.388 --> 14:10.391
‐ On second thought,
put that back on. [laughs]

14:10.475 --> 14:11.059
‐ Al Roker.

14:11.768 --> 14:13.644
I thought he was taller.
[laughs]

14:13.686 --> 14:15.480
‐ Were you in the middle
of doing a, uh...

