14:17.565 --> 14:19.609
‐ You know, Terry
is also a weatherman.

14:19.692 --> 14:20.818
‐ Yep.
‐ Are you really?

14:20.860 --> 14:22.320
‐ Every morning I watch you,

14:22.361 --> 14:24.572
