14:32.246 --> 14:33.539
‐ What happens in your
neck of the woods?

14:33.581 --> 14:35.416
‐ Neck of the woods?
Hello, everybody.

14:35.458 --> 14:37.126
This is Terry Bradshaw
here in Sherman, Texas.

14:37.210 --> 14:39.378
Now, y'all got a little wind
