14:45.051 --> 14:46.344
‐ Are you wearing
pants under that?

14:46.385 --> 14:47.845
‐ Hey, that's not funny.
‐ Sorry.

14:47.887 --> 14:49.388
‐ That is not funny
right there.

14:49.430 --> 14:51.057
‐ And you know funny, too.
That wasn't funny.

14:51.099 --> 14:52.725
‐ I know funny.
‐ Now, Al...

14:52.767 --> 14:54.852
‐ Yes, sir?
‐ I want to present to you,

14:54.894 --> 14:55.853
and you have to put this on.

14:55.895 --> 14:57.021
‐ Oh, of course.

14:57.063 --> 14:58.314
‐ This is a bear's head.
‐ Wow.

14:58.397 --> 14:59.690
‐ All right.
‐ There you go.

14:59.732 --> 15:00.733
‐ They won't notice.

15:00.775 --> 15:02.527
There, the hat. There it is!

15:02.568 --> 15:04.237
‐ I tell you,
you do look better.

15:04.278 --> 15:06.405
‐ And here's
what's happening...

15:06.447 --> 15:08.699
both:
In your neck of the woods.

15:08.741 --> 15:11.577
[upbeat music]

15:11.619 --> 15:13.037
‐ Anybody know
where we're going?

15:13.079 --> 15:14.413
‐ Man, it's cool here.

15:14.455 --> 15:15.790
‐ Yeah, I don't know
where we're going,

15:15.832 --> 15:17.291
but I have got to pee.

15:17.333 --> 15:19.127
‐ This is a bar.
‐ "Klos." K‐L‐O‐S.

15:19.210 --> 15:20.545
‐ It says toilet on it.

15:20.586 --> 15:22.713
You take a squeegee
and I'll get a beer.

15:22.755 --> 15:23.923
‐ Oh!
‐ Oh! What?

15:23.965 --> 15:24.924
‐ Oh!
‐ What?

15:24.966 --> 15:26.092
‐ It‐‐
[chuckles]

15:26.134 --> 15:29.095
