15:35.643 --> 15:36.894
Come and sit down, fellas.

15:36.936 --> 15:38.146
‐ This is great.

15:38.229 --> 15:41.065
[woman screaming]

15:41.107 --> 15:42.483
‐ Wow.
‐ Wow.

15:42.567 --> 15:45.153
‐ Is this weird or what?
‐ Look at this place.

15:45.236 --> 15:47.113
‐ This is the best place
I've ever been.

15:47.155 --> 15:49.782
‐ This place is called Das Klo.

15:49.824 --> 15:52.743
Turns out that
the interpretation in English

15:52.785 --> 15:54.078
