18:25.396 --> 18:26.606
I assume that's
what Henry's parents

18:26.647 --> 18:27.982
were, like, doing for fun,

18:28.065 --> 18:29.900
'cause that's what
everyone was doing.

18:29.942 --> 18:31.360
So, I set this up.

18:31.444 --> 18:33.237
♪ ♪

18:33.279 --> 18:34.905
‐ Hello, guys. Jeff.
‐ How are you?

18:34.947 --> 18:36.574
‐ Welcome to
the Waltzerningestrict.

18:36.616 --> 18:39.410
My name is Geop.
This is my colleague Elisia.

18:39.452 --> 18:40.995
‐ Nice.
‐ And we are both

18:41.078 --> 18:42.747
professional dance instructors.

18:42.830 --> 18:45.833
You've come to a place where
you will dance a waltz today.

18:45.875 --> 18:48.794
[dramatic music]

18:48.836 --> 18:55.926
♪ ♪

18:56.135 --> 18:57.762
This is gonna be a competition.

18:57.803 --> 19:00.306
