a winner at the end.

19:00.348 --> 19:02.933
Grab a partner.
‐ Oh, dibs on the woman.

19:02.975 --> 19:04.226
[both laugh]

19:04.310 --> 19:05.603
Hello there.
‐ Hello.

19:05.645 --> 19:07.688
‐ This is a friendly
competition.

19:07.772 --> 19:09.315
That doesn't mean
I'm not gonna call dibs

19:09.357 --> 19:11.192
on the hot dance instructor.

19:11.275 --> 19:12.443
I ain't gonna win it with

19:12.485 --> 19:14.320
Terry Bradshaw's
hillbilly feet.

19:14.362 --> 19:15.321
‐ Good, you have got
your partner.

19:15.363 --> 19:16.947
‐ Yeah.

19:16.989 --> 19:18.991
‐ So, I want you to practice.
‐ Put her there, partner.

19:19.033 --> 19:21.369
‐ Hello there.
I think she's into me.

19:21.452 --> 19:22.703
Hey, that creep you were
dancing with earlier,

19:22.787 --> 19:24.038
