or something?

19:24.080 --> 19:25.831
‐ Yes.
‐ Oh...

19:25.873 --> 19:26.624
Never mind.

19:27.375 --> 19:28.376
‐ Three with the right,
forward.

19:28.459 --> 19:30.211
End with the left, back.

19:30.294 --> 19:32.296
One, two, three,
and we're here.

19:32.338 --> 19:34.423
‐ Hey. Out of here.

19:34.507 --> 19:36.050
Eat rocks, you old punks.

19:36.133 --> 19:37.968
They're trying to get
a competitive edge.

19:38.010 --> 19:40.471
‐ Can I tempt you to stand
a little closer to each other?

19:40.513 --> 19:41.972
‐ Yes. Yes.

19:42.014 --> 19:45.226
Hey, I'm paired with
the king of fancy footwork.

19:45.309 --> 19:48.479
both: [melodic mumbling]

19:49.522 --> 19:51.148
‐ Uh‐oh,
you messed up that time.

19:51.190 --> 19:52.566
‐ I know.
You know what it's like?

19:52.650 --> 19:54.985
It's like dancing
with Mount Everest.

19:55.027 --> 19:56.445
We have to concentrate,
'cause I know that

19:56.529 --> 19:58.906
Terry is so competitive
to a pulp.

19:58.989 --> 20:00.491
‐ Bill, he's worse.
‐ Yeah.

20:00.533 --> 20:02.410
So, they're working hard.

20:02.493 --> 20:04.912
[relaxing brass music]

20:04.995 --> 20:06.163
‐ This is symbolic.

20:06.247 --> 20:07.873
Terry and I don't need
any waltz instruction.

20:07.915 --> 20:09.792
We'd be better off
going outside

20:09.875 --> 20:11.669
and getting some air
and sharing a cigar.

20:11.711 --> 20:13.003
Now, how are we gonna light it?

20:13.045 --> 20:16.424
‐ Excusez‐moi.
‐ What are you doing?

20:16.507 --> 20:19.427
Where are you going?
Where are you going?

20:19.510 --> 20:21.679
Are you lighting it?

20:21.721 --> 20:22.847
‐ Bill!
‐ What?

20:22.888 --> 20:25.516
‐ I'm trying to light my cigar.

20:25.558 --> 20:28.352
‐ Don't let anybody look.
We're in an alleyway.

20:28.394 --> 20:30.646
‐ Will you quit?
‐ Pass me the ball.

20:30.730 --> 20:33.441
Now you know what
it's like to be a center.

20:33.524 --> 20:36.527
All those years you had
no idea what was going on.

20:36.569 --> 20:38.070
The guy was loving it!

20:38.112 --> 20:40.531
‐ Look.
‐ Success!

20:40.573 --> 20:42.616
‐ Yes! Go get down in there.
‐ No, no, no.

20:42.700 --> 20:44.160
I'll do it from here.

20:44.243 --> 20:46.412
‐ Get close. Get close.
‐ Okay‐‐[muffled] I g‐‐

20:46.454 --> 20:48.914
‐ Pull the match down.
‐ I am!

20:48.956 --> 20:50.416
‐ Suck! Suck!

20:50.458 --> 20:52.042
‐ [muffled]

20:52.084 --> 20:55.212
That was the best thing
that ever happened to me.

20:55.254 --> 20:56.881
My God, you're beautiful.

20:56.922 --> 20:58.215
‐ That was, uh‐‐

20:59.467 --> 21:01.260
actually that was a pretty good
bonding moment for both of us.

21:01.302 --> 21:02.887
[chuckles]

21:02.928 --> 21:05.514
‐ The next problem that needs
solving is who's gonna lead?

21:05.598 --> 21:07.516
‐ Who's the man
and who's the woman?

21:07.600 --> 21:09.852
‐ It would seem likely
that you would be the man,

21:09.935 --> 21:11.562
'cause you're bigger
and taller...

21:11.604 --> 21:13.606
‐ Well...
‐ But that's not the case.

21:13.647 --> 21:14.899
‐ We're not gonna lose.
‐ Come on.

21:14.940 --> 21:16.984
Let's go and see
what we can do.

21:17.067 --> 21:19.236
‐ Let's go. Let's go.
