21:48.599 --> 21:51.101
♪ ♪

21:51.143 --> 21:52.436
[clapping]

21:52.478 --> 21:54.647
‐ Bravo! Bravo!

21:54.688 --> 21:56.357
‐ Next couple, please.
Jeff and Elisia.

21:56.440 --> 21:57.775
‐ You got it.

21:57.817 --> 22:00.319
I love a friendly
competition...

22:00.361 --> 22:02.154
Let's impress
these old geezers.

