22:19.171 --> 22:21.632
♪ ♪

22:21.674 --> 22:24.802
‐ Yes.
‐ Oh, wow.

22:24.844 --> 22:26.804
‐ Oh, yeah!
‐ Too soon. Too soon.

22:26.846 --> 22:28.681
‐ [cackles]
‐ Thank you.

22:28.722 --> 22:31.725
‐ Beautiful.
‐ Yeah.

22:31.809 --> 22:34.645
‐ Thank you. Thank you.
‐ Our last couple.

22:34.687 --> 22:36.146
Bill and Terry, please.

22:36.188 --> 22:38.816
‐ I feel a little shy
about asking you to dance.

22:38.858 --> 22:42.361
I've admired you
for a long time.

22:42.403 --> 22:44.488
Putting my arm around Terry

22:44.530 --> 22:46.323
