Priceless, huh?
‐ Priceless.

24:29.301 --> 24:31.387
‐ That is definitely
not priceless.

24:31.470 --> 24:32.596
I know who did this.

24:32.638 --> 24:35.099
Yep. Smells like hillbilly.

