25:26.066 --> 25:27.693
‐ Bill?
‐ Mm?

25:27.735 --> 25:29.153
♪ ♪

25:29.194 --> 25:32.698
Okay.
Now, listen, I...

25:32.740 --> 25:34.158
Listen, I better‐‐

