‐ What? Did you sleep
in your jacket?

25:35.534 --> 25:37.161
‐ Well, I‐‐
I know, I know.

25:37.202 --> 25:40.289
I was, uh...
‐ What?

25:40.372 --> 25:42.750
‐ I have some
bad news from home.

25:42.791 --> 25:45.252
There's been a death
in the family.

25:45.335 --> 25:48.505
It's my koi.

25:48.547 --> 25:49.715
The fish. The koi.

25:49.757 --> 25:50.883
‐ The death in the family
are your fish?

25:50.924 --> 25:52.760
‐ Yeah.
‐ How many fish?

25:52.843 --> 25:54.386
‐ Could be as many as 30.

25:54.428 --> 25:57.765
‐ How long have you had them?
‐ 15, 20 years.

25:57.848 --> 26:00.768
[slow instrumental music]

26:00.851 --> 26:07.733
♪ ♪

26:07.775 --> 26:10.360
[gong resounds]

26:10.402 --> 26:12.237
