26:15.908 --> 26:16.867
‐ When you feed them, yeah.

26:16.909 --> 26:18.410
‐ They're beautiful.

26:18.452 --> 26:21.288
‐ Do they know you?
‐ They don't say my name.

26:21.330 --> 26:25.250
‐ Or did they know you?
‐ Yeah, but they would react.

26:25.292 --> 26:27.377
They're loving.
The fish are loving.

26:27.419 --> 26:29.088
‐ Yeah. [laughing]
