27:01.411 --> 27:03.539
‐ You're laughing now.
‐ No, I got hay fever in here.

27:03.622 --> 27:06.792
‐ Bill, we are taking
this seriously, okay?

27:06.834 --> 27:08.210
‐ All right.

27:08.293 --> 27:09.920
