happy about right now.

28:57.903 --> 28:59.529
Ooh, I don't know about this.

28:59.571 --> 29:03.533
Hey, seriously, fellas.
Not going over the edge, right?

29:03.575 --> 29:05.869
Man, that's scary.
Are you nervous?

29:05.911 --> 29:10.040
‐ No, man. It's gonna be great.
You're gonna love it.

29:10.123 --> 29:12.876
‐ Help! I may not come back
